\FX[FFF]\AA[FFF]\FFF[1012Furea_0005]\N<Flare>I have a really bad feeling about what lies ahead. Are we
prepared...

(I have a bad feeling about what's ahead... I can't go on
with my stomach like this...)

\FX[FFF]\AA[FFF]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>For the glory of our Black Blizzard group, to instill fear
and despair in humanity, our next target shall be Hinata
City!!

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<Pure Flame>Pure Flame, arriving!! I will burn your evil deeds to
ashes!!
\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\MMM[jump]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>Pu, Pure Flame!? What are you!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<Pure Flame>To stop your evil deeds... I have come to defeat you!!
\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\MMM[jump]\F[1012Furea_0005]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>What are you talking about!! Just a girl in cosplay!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>Heh heh heh, well, whatever. That cosplay girl, she's quite
the beauty. Like a moth to the flame.

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>Hey, capture her! A new sex slave has come to us!! Gangbang
her until she's pregnant!!
\FX[F]\AA[FF]\MM[InL]\F[1012Furea_0013]\FF[4000zakozu]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores>Heh heh heh... come over here... let's have some fun...
\FX[F]\AA[F]\M[jump]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FF[4000zakozu]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<Pure Flame>I won't let you do that!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\MMM[jump]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>!! The Cores, defeated by a civilian!? You, you're not just
some cosplay girl!!

\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<Pure Flame>Haven't I been saying that all along!! Please listen to what
I'm saying!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>!! So, you're the force that Dr. Mad mentioned, opposing
us!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\MMM[no]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>Heh, heh... I thought we were up against some formidable
army... but it's just a young lady...!!

\FX[F]\AA[FFF]\F[1012Furea_0017]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>Luck is on our side!! Guys, if we defeat her, we'll be
promoted in no time!! We can live our lives playing and
raping women!!
\FX[F]\AA[F]\F[1012Furea_0012]\FFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]\N<Pure Flame>It won't be that easy...!! Pure Flame, here I come!!

\FX[F]\AA[FF]\F[1012Furea_00]\FFFF[4001zakozu]\FFFFF[4002zakozu]Hehehe, you've come again!! I'll teach you that no matter
how many times you come, it's useless!!
\FX[FF]\AA[FFFF]\FF[1012Furea_0000]\FFFF[4001zakozu]\N<The Cores Leader>To lose to... to such a cosplay girl... how... gah!!

\FX[FF]\AA[FF]\FF[1012Furea_0000]\N<Flare>...Phew. We've scattered The Cores to some extent, so it
seems we're okay here now.
Do you want to return to the entrance?
